Q: 2024年AAC Jet在North America地区的每月总飞行量是多少？提供环比变化。
SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND b.supplier_id = "1007"
                AND a.dep_area_name = "North America" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, lag( num ) over ( ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        num,
        concat( round(( num - last_num )/ last_num * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;
actual_SQL:

Q: 2024年Adirondack Flying Service在South Asia地区的每月总飞行量是多少？提供环比变化。
SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND b.supplier_id = "1023"
                AND a.dep_area_name = "South Asia" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, lag( num ) over ( ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        num,
        concat( round(( num - last_num )/ last_num * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;
actual_SQL:
SELECT 
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM flight_date) AS year,
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM flight_date) AS month,
    SUM(total_flights) AS monthly_total_flights,
    LAG(SUM(total_flights)) OVER (ORDER BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM flight_date), EXTRACT(MONTH FROM flight_date)) AS previous_month_flights,
    (SUM(total_flights) - LAG(SUM(total_flights)) OVER (ORDER BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM flight_date), EXTRACT(MONTH FROM flight_date))) / NULLIF(LAG(SUM(total_flights)) OVER (ORDER BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM flight_date), EXTRACT(MONTH FROM flight_date)), 0) AS month_over_month_change
FROM 
    flight_data
WHERE 
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM flight_date) = 2024
    AND region = 'South Asia'
    AND airline_name = 'Adirondack Flying Service'
    AND city_id = '1803690220258377730'
GROUP BY 
    year, month
ORDER BY 
    year, month;

    LAG(total_flights, 1) OVER (ORDER BY month) AS previous_month_flights,
